name: Doge Strategy
description: Doge Strategy is a meme-driven digital movement and cryptocurrency project built around the legendary Doge spirit — symbolizing humor, creativity, and decentralized empowerment. It represents the next phase of community-driven innovation in the Dogeverse, where culture meets blockchain. DOGESTR goes beyond being just another meme coin; it’s a strategic ecosystem designed to unite traders, creators, and believers of internet freedom through laughter, virality, and shared growth. The project reimagines what memes can achieve in Web3 by blending entertainment, utility, and decentralized culture into one evolving experience.
